&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;This role can be located in Sydney, New South Wales, Australia; Melbourne, Victoria, Australia.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Primary Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
