&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Overview: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Paraplanner plays a critical role in partnering with Financial Advisers to develop and deliver high-quality, compliant financial advice. Working closely with advisers throughout the advice process, the role provides technical analysis, strategy modelling, investment and insurance research, portfolio reporting and advice document preparation to support quality client outcomes. The Paraplanner contributes to advice development, process improvement and technical capability across the advice team, while helping ensure efficient and consistent advice delivery&lt;/p&gt;
