&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with Financial Advisers to develop and refine client strategies and recommendations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare cashflow projections, modelling and scenario analysis to support client advice strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct research and analysis on investments, wealth platforms, superannuation, retirement strategies and personal insurance solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare insurance comparisons, policy replacement analysis and risk research to support adviser recommendations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare strategic portfolio reviews, investment reports and wholesale client communications.&lt;/li&gt;
